{"tid":2012580,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛既人vs 愛我既人","createTime":"2020-05-11T17:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T00:58:29.000Z","uid":356653,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eed97b23dfd9e780684a1c20d93403e2a779e6a1","tid":2012580,"uid":356653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:11:05.000Z","msg":"一個明知冇結果 佢對自己有好感 但未到要一齊<br />\n但自己好中意佢 好中意同佢相處 覺得好舒服<br />\n但只有自己付岀咁 <br />\n令到自己覺得應唔應該中意就揾佢 唔好諗咩回報<br />\n覺得而加自己付出得開心就得<br />\n<br />\n一個會主動關心自己 覺得對自己幾好<br />\n但佢識得冇上面果個咁耐<br />\n而自己對佢只係覺得幾好傾 覺得佢幾好人<br />\n但一定冇上面果個咁中意 <br />\n所以自己一直都冇好熱情咁對佢 <br />\n因為驚自己比佢覺得有機會 拖咁人<br />\n<br />\n就算唔理我既情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家會點揀<br />\n正評 我愛既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評 愛我既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33b2df4cd28aa2119a0dbe152e61e1e6cf54c6e","tid":2012580,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:11:30.000Z","msg":"林宥嘉相反"},{"pid":"8415849c5a522c919cc0e0661f4088f83873cff7","tid":2012580,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"放過人啦"},{"pid":"2c32e736b271668e66a6b4fa26fc5e5e99d94f4a","tid":2012580,"uid":325491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"愛我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ded7473f194d76f791f61713b170bf5bd07d35b","tid":2012580,"uid":149316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"邊個有錢啲"},{"pid":"462ea14b31183827809ab015355f85ad54a02fac","tid":2012580,"uid":40508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:16:59.000Z","msg":"日久生情的愛總比一見鍾情的愛更持久，所以試吓發掘下愛自己既人既優點。"},{"pid"